## File Patterns
- Pages: `app/[route]/page.tsx`
- Layouts: `app/[route]/layout.tsx`
- API: `app/api/[route]/route.ts`
- Components: `components/[Name].tsx`
- Actions: `lib/actions/[name].ts`
